---
import '../styles/global.css';

const title = "Infinity Digital Proposal";
const description = "Scaling Infinity Digital: The Programmatic SEO Engine";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="description" content={description} />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-50 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-blue-500 selection:text-white">
        
        <!-- Navigation / Brand (Minimal) -->
        <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-slate-900/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-slate-800">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter">
                    <span class="text-white">INFINITY</span><span class="text-blue-500">DIGITAL</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
                    Executive Brief
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-24">
            
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col justify-center mb-24 fade-in">
                <div class="inline-block mb-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-500/30 text-blue-400 text-xs font-mono tracking-widest uppercase w-fit">
                    Confidential Proposal
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-slate-200 to-slate-400">
                    Scaling <br/>
                    Infinity Digital
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-400 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-6">
                    The Programmatic SEO Engine: <br/>
                    <span class="text-white font-medium">Moving from Manual Labor to Exponential Leverage.</span>
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 1: The Problem -->
            <section class="mb-32 space-y-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-amber-400 mr-4 text-4xl">01.</span>
                    The Problem: Manual SEO is Linear
                </h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        In the current landscape, agency growth is bottlenecked by human output. 
                        Writing high-quality content for every possible local search intent is mathematically impossible with a manual approach.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Consider the "Long Tail" of search. A potential customer isn't just searching for "Ford Dealer". 
                        They are searching for <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono bg-blue-900/20 px-1">"Ford F-150 Lease Sugar Land"</span> or <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono bg-blue-900/20 px-1">"Used Honda Civic Katy TX"</span>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Capturing this intent manually would require thousands of hours of writing. It's a linear path that cannot scale.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 2: The Solution -->
            <section class="mb-32 space-y-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-blue-500 mr-4 text-4xl">02.</span>
                    The Solution: The pSEO Factory
                </h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        We don't write pages. We build engines that generate them.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 my-8">
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                            <div class="text-green-400 text-2xl">âœ“</div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2">Proof of Concept</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-400">
                                    We just built <span class="text-white font-bold">3,000+ high-quality pages</span> in under 12 hours across 3 distinct industries (Appliance Repair, Automotive OBD2, B2B SaaS).
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        This infrastructure allows Infinity Digital to dominate niche markets instantly, deploying thousands of landing pages that are perfectly optimized for conversion.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3: Auto Strategy -->
            <section class="mb-32 space-y-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-amber-400 mr-4 text-4xl">03.</span>
                    The Dealership Matrix
                </h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        Applying this to the automotive sector creates an unfair advantage. We utilize a 3-dimensional matrix to capture every ounce of search volume.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8 text-center font-mono text-sm">
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
                            <div class="text-blue-400 mb-2">DIMENSION 1</div>
                            <div class="text-white font-bold">MODEL</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Raptor, F-150, Mustang</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
                            <div class="text-amber-400 mb-2">DIMENSION 2</div>
                            <div class="text-white font-bold">SERVICE</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Oil Change, Lease, Repair</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
                            <div class="text-green-400 mb-2">DIMENSION 3</div>
                            <div class="text-white font-bold">LOCATION</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Katy, Sugar Land, Woodlands</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p>
                        <strong>The Result:</strong> Hyper-specific pages like <span class="text-white font-bold">"Oil Change for Raptor in Katy"</span> that rank #1 because they perfectly match the user's query.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <section class="text-center py-16 border-t border-slate-800">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Ready to Deploy?</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                    The infrastructure is built. The data pipelines are ready. It's time to launch the pilot program.
                </p>
                
                <a href="#" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition-all duration-200 bg-blue-600 font-pj rounded-full focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 hover:scale-105">
                    Launch Pilot Program
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 -mr-1 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="absolute -inset-3 rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 blur-lg transition-opacity duration-200"></div>
                </a>
            </section>

        </main>

        <footer class="border-t border-slate-800 py-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
                &copy; 2025 Infinity Digital Consulting. Confidential & Proprietary.
            </p>
        </footer>

	</body>
</html>
